{"word":"κατασπουδάζομαι","slug":"κατασπουδάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατασπουδάζομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>with aor1 and <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, <i>to be very earnest</i> or <i>serious</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>οὐδαμῶς κατεσπουδασμένος ἀνήρ</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/>"}]}